        The second direction pushed HFO in a direction that we felt was more inline with both where we discovered they were at but also where they envisioned HFO going in the future. A more modern and friendly approach which spoke to the uniqueness of HFO brand. The typography is rounded, open which gives this direction an approachable yet professional look and feel. The logo incorporates a wordmark that visually represents parts of a whole. This visual speaks to the collaborative nature of the HFO culture, and also nods toward apartment properties.
